special_powers.name: SHIFTING FOCUS - BATMAN
special_powers.description: Give Batman a free action if he began your turn on the map. Replace him with another character with this trait on the same click number.

special_powers.name: THEY DON'T EVEN REALIZE HOW MUCH THEY NEED ME
special_powers.description: Batman can use Perplex. UNIQUE MODIFIER - He may use Perplex to target all other friendly characters within 4 squares and line of fire, choosing the same single combat value other than damage to modify.

special_powers.name: SHIFTING FOCUS - SUPERMAN
special_powers.description: Give Superman a free action if he began your turn on the map. Replace him with another character with this trait on the same click number.

special_powers.name: DEEP IMPACT
special_powers.description: Superman can use Precision Strike and Quake. When Superman uses Leap/Climb, after actions resolve he may use Quake as a free action.

special_powers.name: BRACELET BASH
special_powers.description: Wonder Woman can use Force Blast. When Wonder Woman misses with a close attack, after actions resolve she may use Force Blast as a free action.

special_powers.name: TEAM TRANSPORTER
special_powers.description: When Green Lantern is the only character on your force with the Green Lantern Team Ability symbol and uses the Carry ability, you may roll a d6: 5: One carried higher-point character may be given a non-free action. 6: Up to two carried higher-point characters may each be given a non-free action.

special_powers.name: FOR DIVINE GLORY
special_powers.description: Templar can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast. When he does and the target has the Monster or Mystical keyword, this action doesn't count against your action total.

special_powers.name: THE STRENGTH I NEED AT A TERRIBLE COST
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, you may roll a d6 that can't be rerolled and add The Bat's click number. On a result of 7 or more, you replace The Bat with ew020 The Joker Creature on the same click number plus 2.

special_powers.name: APPREHEND THE ALIENS!

special_powers.name: HIGH NOON

special_powers.name: ELECTRO-STUNNER
special_powers.description: Super Men can use Incapacitate. When he uses it as part of a close combat action, he may target up to 2 adjacent characters.

special_powers.name: HIGH NOON
special_powers.description: If Diana Prince (Justice Rider) is the last character with this trait to hit an opposing character with a range attack, until your next turn, if the hit character makes a range attack, Diana Prince (Justice Rider) must be one of its targets.

special_powers.name: NEW SHERIFF IN TOWN
special_powers.description: Diana Prince (Justice RIder) can use Leadership. UNIQUE MODIFIER - When she does and succeeds, other friendly characters that share a keyword with her modify their attack and defense values by +1 until your next turn.

special_powers.name: HIGH NOON
special_powers.description: If Kid Flash (Justice Rider) is the last character with this trait to hit an opposing character with a range attack, until your next turn, if the hit character makes a range attack, Kid Flash (Justice Rider) must be one of its targets.

special_powers.name: QUICKEST SHOT IN THE WEST
special_powers.description: Kid Flash (Justice Rider) can use Hypersonic Speed. When he does, he doesn't halve his range value.

special_powers.name: ALWAYS GET MY MAN
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, choose an opposing character. If John Jones (Justice Rider) would get a second action token while adjacent to the chosen character, instead he doesn't get an action token.

special_powers.name: HIGH NOON
special_powers.description: If John Jones (Justice Rider) is the last character with this trait to hit an opposing character with a range attack, until your next turn, if the hit character makes a range attack, John Jones (Justice Rider) must be one of its targets.

special_powers.name: MANHUNTING LAWMAN
special_powers.description: John Jones (Justice Rider) can use Charge and Plasticity.

special_powers.name: THERE MUST ALWAYS BE A BATMAN
special_powers.description: When Batman would be KO'd, you may instead KO another friendly character with a point value of 25 or more and turn Batman to click #1.

special_powers.name: I PLEAD GUILTY, YOUR HONOR
special_powers.description: Whenever Superman deals damage from an attack, you may choose to deal an amount of damage from 1 to his damage value instead of normal damage. If Superman KO's an opposing character, after actions resolve, deal him 1 unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: BRACELETS
special_powers.description: Wonder Woman can use Super Senses, but only when targeted by a range attack.

special_powers.name: CREATED EQUAL

special_powers.name: I PRAY ATHENA GUIDES US IN DOING WHAT IS RIGHT FOR MANKI-... UHM... HUMANITY
special_powers.description: Wonder Woman can use Leadership. When she does, increase the result by 1 for each adjacent friendly character with the Amazon keyword.

special_powers.name: THE POWER BATTERY IS DRAINING... I HAVE LIMITED TIME
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, place 8 Battery tokens on this card. When Green Lantern attacks, remove a battery token. When there are no Battery tokens on this card, Green Lantern can't make range attacks or use powers or abilities.

special_powers.name: TO FIGHT DARKSEID AND APOKOLIPS
special_powers.description: Green Lantern can use Pulse Wave and Telekinesis.

special_powers.name: SAVING THE PRESIDENT
special_powers.description: Once per game, if another friendly character within 10 squares and line of fire would be hit by a range attack, you may place The Flash in a square adjacent to the target and that attack misses that target. If you do, for the rest of the game, The Flash's speed value becomes 0 and he can use Sidestep and Outwit.

special_powers.name: HEAVEN GRANTS ME PROTECTION
special_powers.description: If Oliver Queen, Templar would take damage from the Mystics team ability, instead heal him 1 click.

special_powers.name: MAGIC ARROWS
special_powers.description: Oliver Queen, Templar can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast. When he targets a character with the Monster or Mystical keyword, he modifies his attack value by +1. If the target has both keywords, he also modifies his damage value by +1.

special_powers.name: THE CREATURE, IT'S... YOU, DR. WAYNE!
special_powers.description: When The Joker Creature replaces ew007 The Bat, give each other character within 6 squares and line of fire an action token.

special_powers.name: HE STALKED THEM AT NIGHT
special_powers.description: The Joker Creature deals penetrating damage to characters with 2 action tokens. When The Joker Creature hits a character, after actions resolve give that character an action token if The Joker Creature occupies hindering terrain.

special_powers.name: BIZARRO D.N.A. DEGRADATION
special_powers.description: Bizarro Police takes a maximum of 1 damage from attacks. When Bizarro Police is hit with an attack and his defense value is equal to the attacker's attack total, KO Bizarro Police. This power can't be countered or ignored.

special_powers.name: CALCULATED YOUR DEFEAT
special_powers.description: Clockwork Man can use Precision Strike. UNIQUE MODIFIER - When he hits an opposing character, that character modifies its attack value by -1 until your next turn.

special_powers.name: ENHANCED ELECTRO-STUNNER
special_powers.description: Pete Ross can use Incapacitate. When he does, also target all opposing characters adjacent to the original target.

special_powers.name: FREEDOM HAS A PRICE. MINE IS TWO HUNDRED MILLION.
special_powers.description: STOP. Opposing characters within 4 squares can use Incapacitate and Toughness.

special_powers.name: AVATAR OF DARKNESS
special_powers.description: Other friendly characters can use the Batman Ally team ability. When Nekhrun, The Bat-God is KO'd by an opponent's attack, for the rest of the game other friendly characters can't be targeted by opposing characters 4 or more squares away.

special_powers.name: BURSTS OF INCREDIBLE SPEED
special_powers.description: When Jakita Wagner has no action tokens, she can use Hypersonic Speed and modifies her speed value by +2. When she has one action token, she can use Charge and modifies her speed value by +1.

special_powers.name: PLANETARY: ARCHAEOLOGISTS OF THE IMPOSSIBLE

special_powers.name: YOU THINK I CARE HOW MANY OF YOU I KILL?

At the beginning of your next turn, deal Green Lantern 1 unavoidable damage, even if this power is lost.

special_powers.name: ALL THIS POWER, LIMITED BY MY WILL

special_powers.name: EMERALD KNIGHT

special_powers.name: FROM AN ALTERNATE EARTH

special_powers.name: MY BODY ADAPTED TO LIVING ON KRYPTON

special_powers.name: YOU WON'T SHOOT, IF YOU KNOW WHAT'S GOOD FOR YOU

special_powers.description: Sergeant Kent can use Defend. Opposing characters can't ignore Sergeant Kent for line of fire purposes.

special_powers.name: GENIE OF THE LAMP
special_powers.description: Give Al Jhor Dan a free action. Choose a standard power and choose one of the following: "wing symbol", "dolphin symbol", "giant symbol", or "tiny symbol". Al Jhor Dan can use the chosen power and has the chosen symbol until your next turn.

special_powers.name: 1001 (KNIGHTS OF EMPIRES)
special_powers.description: Al Jhor Dan can use Perplex. If he uses Perplex to modify the same character and same value as during your last turn, he can modify it by +2 or -2 instead.

special_powers.name: FROM AN ALTERNATE EARTH
special_powers.description: If this character is on your sideline, you may give a free action to a friendly character named The Joker or Sinestro that's equal or more points. Replace that character with this character on the same click number.

special_powers.name: HERO OF QWARD
special_powers.description: Sinestro can use Perplex, but only to decrease combat values.

special_powers.name: HERO OF THE CORPS
special_powers.description: Sinestro can use Pulse Wave and has the Green Lantern team ability.

special_powers.name: ULTIMATE NEMESIS
special_powers.description: Opposing characters with the Batman Family, Gotham City, or Green Lantern Corps keywords modify their attack value by -1. If they target Sinestro, modify their attack value by an additional -1.

special_powers.name: ONE LAST EARTHLY MISSION
special_powers.description: When another friendly character is KO'd, place a Resurrection marker in a square they last occupied. Give Green Lantern a free action when she is adjacent to a Resurrection marker, you may choose the name of a friendly character with a point value of 10 or more that has been KO'd and hasn't yet been chosen this game. Replace the Resurrection marker with a KO'd character with that name and give Green Lantern an action token, if possible. Turn the KO'd character to any click it could have been on this game. At the beginning of your next turn, remove that character from the game but don't score it.

special_powers.name: CAPTAIN OF THE FLYING FOX
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, place adjacent a Robin Redblade bystander. Leatherwing can use the Carry ability to carry up to 4 characters with the Pirate keyword.

special_powers.name: DOWN FROM THE RIGGING AND ACROSS THE DECK
special_powers.description: Leatherwing can use Leap/Climb and Sidestep. When Leatherwing uses Leap/Climb and moves half his speed value or less, after actions resolve he may make a range attack.

special_powers.name: FLOURISH OF THE BLADE AND CLOAK
special_powers.description: Leatherwing can use Blades/Claws/Fangs and Smoke Cloud. When he uses Blades/Claws/Fangs, after actions resolve he can use Smoke Cloud as a free action.

special_powers.name: INVESTIGATING PLANETARY
special_powers.description: Opposing characters within 4 squares and line of fire can't use Outwit or Perplex.

special_powers.name: SWORDS MANIFESTED FROM MY WRISTBANDS
special_powers.description: Diana Prince can use Blades/Claws/Fangs. Give Diana Prince a close combat action to make a close attack targeting each opposing character within 2 squares and line of fire.

special_powers.name: AVENGE THE AMAZONS, BUT REMEMBER THEIR HEART

special_powers.name: WE WILL MAKE THINGS RIGHT AGAIN
special_powers.description: King Aquaman's combat values can only be modified by power or abilities from characters with the "Kingdom Come team ability symbol". King Aquaman's powers and abilities can only be countered by characters with the "Kingdom Come team ability symbol".

special_powers.name: I HAVE RESPONSIBILITIES YOU CANNOT EVEN DREAM OF
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, you may place a water terrain marker in any square of clear terrain within 8 squares. Give King Aquaman a free action and choose an opposing character that occupies water terrain within 8 squares. Place that character into an adjacent square.

special_powers.name: THE BIG FREEZE
special_powers.description: Once per game, give Elijah Snow a free action. For the rest of the game, while Elijah Snow is on the map other characters that can't use the Flight ability can only move in a direct path.

special_powers.name: CHILL IN YOUR BONES
special_powers.description: Give Elijah Snow a free action and choose one that hasn't been chosen yet this game: Power, Close Combat, Range Combat, or Move. Until your next turn, when an opposing character is given an action of the chosen type, after actions resolve give that character an action token. If you can't, deal them 1 unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: PLANETARY: ARCHAEOLOGISTS OF THE IMPOSSIBLE
special_powers.description: Once per turn, Elijah Snow can use either Outwit or Perplex.

special_powers.name: THE DARK KNIGHT RETURNS: WE'VE ALWAYS BEEN CRIMINALS
special_powers.description: When Batman occupies clear terrain, and is given a non-free action, after actions resolve you may place him in printed hindering terrain within 4 squares and line of fire.

special_powers.name: STRIKING TERROR... BEST PART OF THE JOB
special_powers.description: Batman can use Outwit and Shape Change.

special_powers.name: COMPUTER CLASSES, DUH
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game place adjacent either the Batcycle or Batwing bystander. When that bystander is KO'd, after actions resolve place the other bystander adjacent.

special_powers.name: THE DARK KNIGHT RETURNS: GET SEEN AND YOU'RE FIRED
special_powers.description: When Robin occupies clear terrain, she can use Shape Change. When she occupies hindering terrain, she can use Perplex but only to target another character occupying hindering terrain.

special_powers.name: THE DARK KNIGHT RETURNS: NOT HIDING ANYMORE
special_powers.description: When Green Arrow occupies clear terrain, he can use Sidestep and opposing characters can't draw lines of fire to him unless they are within three squares of him or he has 2 action tokens.

special_powers.name: ...IT STILL HURTS WHEN IT'S COLD
special_powers.description: Green Arrow can't make range attacks when he has 1 action token.

special_powers.name: KRYPTONITE ARROWS
special_powers.description: When Green Arrow hits with a ranged attack, the hit target can't use defense powers until your next turn. If the hit target has the Kryptonian keyword also give it an action token.

special_powers.name: A SYMBOL OF AUTHORITY... AND OBEDIENCE
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, you may roll a d6. 5-6: Superman's powers can't be countered and his attack rolls can't be rerolled by opponents until your next turn. 3-4: You may remove an action token from him. 1: He can't be moved or placed until your next turn.

special_powers.name: WE MUST NOT REMIND THEM THAT GIANTS WALK THE EARTH
special_powers.description: Superman can use Charge and Stealth. If Superman began the turn occupying hindering terrain, don't halve his speed value when using Charge this turn.

special_powers.name: SOLAR POWER STORED BY A SUFFERING WORLD
special_powers.description: Give Superman a free action when he occupies printed outdoor hindering terrain and roll a d6. Heal him of half the result and put a Scoured marker in that square. Squares with Scoured markers in them are considered clear terrain instead of hindering terrain for the rest of the game.

special_powers.name: REVERT TO RICK
special_powers.description: Hourman can use Charge and Sidestep. At the beginning of your turn, remove an Hour token. When Hourman has no Hour tokens turn him to click #2.

special_powers.name: HOUR OF POWER
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn give Hourman an Hour token. When Hourman has three Hour tokens, turn him to click #9.

special_powers.name: GRAPPLING GUN
special_powers.description: Batman can use Improved Movement: Elevated, Hindering.

special_powers.name: LEADER OF HEROES
special_powers.description: Superman can use Leadership. When he does and succeeds, other friendly characters that share a keyword with Superman modify their defense value by +1 until your next turn.

special_powers.name: LASSO-WIELDING WARRIOR
special_powers.description: Wonder Woman can use Charge, Flurry and Plasticity.

special_powers.name: BEWARE MY POWER
special_powers.description: Give Green Lantern a free action and choose: Penetrating/Psychic Blast, Perplex, or Telekinesis. Green Lantern can use the chosen power until your next turn.

special_powers.name: BRACE YOURSELF, WE'RE GOING TO MOVE QUICKLY

special_powers.name: REVERBERATING MULTITHREADED ION CANNONS
special_powers.description: Cyborg can use Energy Explosion and Penetrating/Psychic Blast.

special_powers.name: MAGNETIC SKIN
special_powers.description: The Skyscraper Wonder Woman can use Plasticity and Sidestep. When an adjacent opposing character fails to break away, after actions resolve give it an action token. If you can't, deal it 1 unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: THE TRIAL OF ICE
special_powers.description: When The Skyscraper Wonder Woman hits an opposing character, after actions resolve choose one: give that character an action token; -or- place that character in any square within 5 squares of The Skyscraper Wonder Woman that's closer to your starting area than its current square.

special_powers.name: COLOSSAL RETALIATION: BURY YOU IN SAND
special_powers.description: Give The Skyscraper Wonder Woman a free action if no other Colossal Retaliation power has been activated this turn and choose an opposing character that attacked The Skyscraper Wonder Woman or damaged a friendly character since your last turn. Place The Skyscraper Wonder Woman such that it can make a close attack targeting the chosen character and also target all other characters within 2 squares of the target. Hit characters are each dealt 3 damage instead of normal damage and can't move or be placed or make range attacks during their next turns.

special_powers.name: COLOSSAL INDIFFERENCE
special_powers.description: STOP. The Skyscraper Wonder Woman can use Toughness. If The Skyscraper Wonder Woman began the game on the 15-point starting line, she can't attack smaller characters except via Colossal Retaliation.
